verbose_text: Lin et al. were successful in cloning Toll like receptor-2 (TLR2) from 3T3-L1 adipocytes, and they showed that adipocytic TLR2 synthesis increases upon stimulation with LPS and tumor necrosis factor (TNF), respectively [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: TLR2 synthesis increases upon stimulation with LPS and tumor necrosis factor
